{
  "stem": "1895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those where the so-called Einsatzgruppen who came for special action.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember looking at them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember the-- that they were youngsters, very young, very blond, very clean-looking, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with their helmets and the chin straps and the backpacks and their ready guns, as if on a holy mission--",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in a combat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like it was a combat-- it was a combat duty, like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And their facial expression was you either do it or you're dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember once in Pionki, I had befriended a young boy named Becker, a German young boy named Becker.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very good friends for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the time, I remember thinking, is this young Becker among these Germans?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I remembered another thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I wrote this memoir, I remembered reading a statement by Reagan at the time of the Bitburg controversy where he said that there are no Germans left who had taken part in these things.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Evidently he already had Alzheimer's then, because, you know, I remember looking at these youngsters, and they were not much older than 16, 17, or 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was no way in the world that these people didn't survive to this day, because they weren't much older than I was at the time, maybe two, three years older.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And yet he had the gall to say that there are no Germans alive who had participated in these things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said that in-- in the 1980s, in the mid-1980s.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
